  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'vertical-align:top;margin:0in;padding:0pt;width=
:3.1409in;
  height:1.8763in'>
  <p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>On May 4th, =
2010,
  I returned to a 12-step meeting that I had attended regularly, for the fi=
rst
  time in months.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>¬† </span>A friend that I
  trusted well, asked to speak with me privately afterwards.<span
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>¬† </span>He told me that God had given him a =
message
  in meditation one day, several months previously.<span
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>¬† </span>He said that God told him that I was
  thinking about doing something, and for him to tell me, when he saw me ag=
ain,
  that God said for me to go ahead and do it.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:ye=
s'>¬†
  </span></p>
  </td>
  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'vertical-align:top;margin:0in;padding:0pt;width=
:.077in;
  height:1.8756in;font-size:1pt'>
  <p style=3D'font-size:1pt'></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'vertical-align:top;margin:0in;padding:0pt;width=
:1px;
  height:.1798in;font-size:1pt'>
  <p style=3D'font-size:1pt'>&nbsp;</p>
  </td>
  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'vertical-align:top;margin:0in;padding:0pt;width=
:3.1409in;
  height:.1798in;font-size:1pt'>
  <p style=3D'font-size:1pt'></p>
  </td>
  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'vertical-align:top;margin:0in;padding:0pt;width=
:.077in;
  height:.1798in;font-size:1pt'>
  <p style=3D'font-size:1pt'></p>
